'''油渣'''（Cracklings (美式英语), crackling (英式英语)），是[[猪油|猪油]]等提炼动物油脂后残留的残渣。<ref name="davidson">[[Alan_Davidson_(food_writer)|Alan Davidson]], ''[[The_Oxford_Companion_to_Food|The Oxford Companion to Food]]'', ''s.v.''</ref>

猪、鹅、鸡、牛、羊等都是油渣的重要来源。<ref>Federal Board for Vocational Education, "The Home Project as a Phase of Vocational Agricultural Education", Bulletin no. 21, Agricultural Series no. 3 (September 1918)
[https://www.google.com/books/edition/Bulletin/5kLyAAAAMAAJ?hl=en&gbpv=1&bsq=cracklings p. 85]</ref>
